{"title":"阶级弟兄","authors":["张昆华"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":7,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级弟兄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张昆华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春水一般的月光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾泻在雄伟的山岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进攻演习还没有开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩蔽部里掌声震响……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军身披一领斗篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻走到掩蔽部门口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜风送出一个故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那絮絮的语声多么耳熟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“刚刚开始爬雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团长突然生了病。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通讯员照顾着首长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一对雄鹰飞越了峰顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“眼睫毛还沾着冰花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就踏上茫茫的草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那暴风雨的深夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电照射出一幅剪影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“生病的团长反而背着通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讯员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步跟紧北上的队伍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个人只留下一双脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级弟兄的情谊照亮了征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"途……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们听完团长讲的故"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个眼中饱含了泪水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“为啥通讯员要让团长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那亲爱的首长他是谁？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“通讯员如今还感到惭愧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团长就是我们将军……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在门口的将军再也忍不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手指着团长跨进掩蔽部："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小鬼，大渡河边负了伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为啥一直没有讲？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶持我翻过大雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到你昏迷在草地上。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们的心里明白了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围上去拥抱团长和将军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命军队是大家庭啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首长、士兵比弟兄还亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春水一般的月光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾泻在雄伟的山岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群山的松林荡出涛声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把光荣传统纵情歌唱！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}